org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.registry

Interface IQuerySpecificationRegistryEntry

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IProvider<IQuerySpecification<?>>, IQuerySpecificationProvider

    public interface IQuerySpecificationRegistryEntry
extends IQuerySpecificationProvider
    The query specification registry entry interface can return the identifier of the source that added it to the registry. It is provider based and can delay class loading of the wrapped IQuerySpecification until needed.
    Since:
    1.3
